monsterz: monsterz (Puzzle game, similar to Bejeweled or Zookeeper)
monsterz:
monsterz: Monsterz is a little arcade puzzle game, similar to the famous
monsterz: Bejeweled or Zookeeper. The goal of the game is to create rows of
monsterz: similar monsters, either horizontally or vertically. The only allowed
monsterz: move is the swap of two adjacent monsters, on the condition that it
monsterz: creates a row of three or more. When alignments are cleared, pieces
monsterz: fall from the top of the screen to fill the board again. Chain
monsterz: reactions earn you even more points.
monsterz: http://sam.zoy.org/monsterz/
